1779:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TIM commutation event sequence.
1780:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
